Package com.palantir.curatortestrule

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ZooKeeperRuleConfig
    Defines an interface to get a ServerCnxnFactory.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultZooKeeperRuleConfig
    Default implementation of ZooKeeperRuleConfig which uses a NoJMXZooKeeperServer and uses temp directories for the FileTxnSnapLog.
    LocalZooKeeperRule
    A simple ZooKeeperRule that gets a ServerCnxnFactory from ZooKeeperRuleConfig on the port before running the statement, and shutdowns the ServerCnxnFactory after the statement.
    NoJMXZooKeeperServer
    A subclass of ZooKeeperServer that skips JMX related operations.
    SharedZooKeeperRule
    A ZooKeeperRule that shares servers based on the port number specified in the constructor.
    ZooKeeperRule
    JUnit rule to create a zookeeper server and to create curator instances to connect to the zookeeper server.
